    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
      {lang === 'zh' ? (
        <>
          项目页面模板源自 <a href="https://github.com/nerfies/nerfies.github.io" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Nerfies</a>。本网站根据 <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">CC BY-SA 4.0</a> 许可协议授权。
        </>
      ) : (
        <>
          Project page template from <a href="https://github.com/nerfies/nerfies.github.io" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Nerfies</a>. Licensed under <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">CC BY-SA 4.0</a>.
